  • Method Details

    • cancel

      void cancel(javafx.event.ActionEvent event) throws IOException
      If the New Appointment window was opened from the main window, returns to the main window when the cancel button is pressed. If the New Appointment window was opened from the Customer Appointments window, closes the window when the cancel button is pressed.
      Throws:
      IOException

    • saveAppointment

      void saveAppointment(javafx.event.ActionEvent event) throws IOException, SQLException
      Validates the fields in the new appointment window, and commits the new appointment to the database when the save button is pressed. If the New Appointment window was opened from the main window, returns to the main window when complete. If the New Appointment window was opened from the Customer Appointments window, closes the window when complete.
      Throws:
      IOException
      SQLException
